      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Type Definition Library\n\nA type definition declares what the legend should show and what consumers should trust.\n\nCommitted v1 fields:\n- `name`\n- `key`\n- `classRef`\n- `meaning`\n- `description`\n- `category`\n- `status`\n\nOpen the template to author one, or bridge the class directly when you need a reusable declared type node."
      }
